      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like i'm just going through the motions at this point. like i'm a tourist in my own life, just looking at things through a window. everything is so heavy. like even a beautiful view just feels like more noise i don't want to deal with. is it normal to feel like you've reached the end of your line?",
